  # I Tested Cursor, GitHub Copilot, and Claude Code. One Wins Clearly.
  
  ## Three weeks, one real codebase, and a result I did not expect going in.
  
  [![inprogrammer](https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fill:64:64/1*J7jk5vCGbEhewExz70dAAg.png)](https://medium.com/@inprogrammer?source=post_page---byline--a6f19828f32f---------------------------------------)
  
